  "title": "Junior Conveyancing Lawyer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Position title: Junior Conveyancing Lawyer</strong></p><p>Working Days: 5 days<br />Working Timing: 9:00 am to 6:00 pm<br />Working Location: Telok Ayer<br />Salary: From $5,500</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities & Duties:</strong></p><ul><li>Prepare and review legal documents related to property transactions. These documents include sale and purchase agreements and loan agreements.</li><li>You will provide advice to clients on all aspects of buying or selling property. This includes legal issues, financial considerations, and contract matters.</li><li>Engage in negotiations with the other party’s lawyer for the Option to Purchase (OTP). Provide advice to clients on the conveyancing process and their rights and obligations.</li><li>Liaise with various parties involved in the transaction, including real estate agents, mortgage lenders, and other relevant stakeholders.</li></ul><p><strong>Qualifications and Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Bachelor's Degree in Law </li><li>0-3 years of Post-Qualification Experience (PQE) in conveyancing or related<br />legal work.</li><li>Familiarity with property laws and conveyancing procedures.</li></ul><p><br />Tan Yen Zhen (Chen Yan Zhen) Reg No: R25138932</p><p>The SupremeHR Advisory Pte Ltd EA No: 14C7279</p>",
